made 2020/05/23, Katzenelson-adjacent family recipe

2T butter
8 oz cream cheese
15.25 oz whole kernel corn, drained
14.75 oz cream-style corn
8.5 oz corn muffin mix
2 eggs
1C shredded cheddar

melt butter in microwave, add cream cheese, microwave until soft, mix the two
add corn, other corn, muffin mix, and eggs, mix
dump into greased 9x13
sprinkle with cheddar
40 min at 350F

